{"word":"G4370 - προστρέχω - prostréchō - pros-trekh'-o - Run","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προστρέχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prostréchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-trekh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Run</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஓடிவா, ஒடிப்போ"},{"paragraph":"to run to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G5143 - τρέχω - tréchō - trekh'-o/5143\">G5143</a> (including its alternate); to <i>run towards</i>, that is, <i>hasten</i> to meet or join: - run (thither to, to).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}